A place to store hotkeys!

TERMINAL HOTKEYS
Ctrl+L --> Clear Screen
Ctrl+A --> Jump to beginning of line
Ctrl+E --> Go to end of line
Ctrl+D --> Delete right of cursor
Ctrl+K --> Kill entire line from cursor
Ctrl+U --> Clear entire line 

ITERM Hotkeys
Option+Cmd+C --> include styles/fonts in copy


VIM HOTKEYS
<leader>=" "

// Copy yanked to temp, so you can paste across terminals
<leader>y
<leader>p

// VIM .ideavimrc HOTKEYS (For INTELLIJ)
gb --> go back
gf --> go forward
<leader>r --> Recent Files
<leader>l --> Recent Locations

INTELLIJ HOTKEYS
// CODE
Ctrl+Enter --> populate possible props options
Ctrl+Z --> toggle focus mode
Ctrl+Cmd+F --> toggle full screen mode
Cmd+1 --> shortcut to projects pane
Ctrl+T --> go to terminal
Shift+Esc --> close terminal
Cmd+D --> compare selected files
Enter --> Normal mode - go to next line while staying in normal mode
Shift+Enter --> Normal mode - insert line below
Option+Tab --> Toggle between splitters in split pane
Option+Shift+Tab --> Toggle previous splitter
Cmd+Cmd(hold) --> While in focus mode - Quickly show left menu bar

// From Sublime
vil --> select line
Ctrl+Cmd+G --> select all
Cmd+G --> select next
Shift+Cmd+G --> select previous


TERRAFORM HOTKEYS
tg=terragrunt
tga=terragrunt apply
tgc=terragrunt console
tgd=terragrunt destroy
tgf=terragrunt fmt
tgi=terragrunt init
tgo=terragrunt output
tgp=terragrunt plan
tgv=terragrunt validate

MAC OS SYSTEM HOTKEYS
Cmd+Delete - Delete from cursor to BOL
Option+Delete - Delete word
Fn+Delete - Delete char right of cursor

Cmd+Option+. - view hidden files for finder MacOS
